c: 22
v: 52
t: "Ife sitidatumizepo Mtumwi kapena Mneneri, iwe usanadze, koma iye amati akamalakatula chivumbulutso kapena kulalikira, Satana anali kuonjezera bodza. Koma Mulungu amachotsa zonse zimene Satana waikamo. Motero Mulungu amakhazikitsa chivumbulutso chake ndipo Mulungu ndi wodziwa ndi waluntha"